other_rules.name: Wireless Block List Default
other_rules.conditions: Radius.NAS-Port-Type equals Wireless - IEEE 802.11 AND IdentityGroup.Name equals Endpoint Identity Groups:Blocked List

other_rules.name: Unknown_Compliance_Redirect
other_rules.conditions: Network Access.AuthenticationStatus equals AuthenticationPassed AND Session.PostureStatus equals Unknown

other_rules.name: NonCompliant_Devices_Redirect
other_rules.conditions: Network Access.AuthenticationStatus equals AuthenticationPassed AND Session.PostureStatus equals NonCompliant

other_rules.name: Compliant_Devices_Access
other_rules.conditions: Network Access.AuthenticationStatus equals AuthenticationPassed AND Session.PostureStatus equals Compliant

other_rules.name: Employee_EAP-TLS
other_rules.conditions: Normalised Radius.RadiusFlowType equals Wireless802_1x AND EndPoints.BYODRegistration equals Yes AND Network Access.EapAuthentication equals EAP-TLS AND CERTIFICATE.Subject Alternative Name equals Calling-Station-ID

other_rules.name: Employee_Onboarding
other_rules.conditions: Normalised Radius.RadiusFlowType equals Wireless802_1x AND Network Access.EapAuthentication equals EAP-MSCHAPv2

other_rules.name: Wi-Fi_Guest_Access
other_rules.conditions: Network Access.UseCase equals Guest Flow AND Normalised Radius.RadiusFlowType equals WirelessMAB
